  "body": "### Version of Hardhat\n\n2.19.3\n\n### What happened?\n\n**Issues:**\r\nWhen doing basic deployments on different networks, either transactions hang or don't get complete at all\r\n\r\n**Tests Performed**\r\n```\r\nEthereum\r\n(Need more ETH)\r\n\r\nPolygon\r\n✅ Hardhat Viem - 0xe43f591ad474ca29deb4d0c89702539d66849b7f\r\n❌ Hardhat Ethers6 - (Script Hangs - No Tx Hash)\r\n✅ Foundry - 0xbC7D321D31e64733Db7a1e4C9dD33941D68fEbB7\r\n\r\nGoerli\r\n✅ Hardhat Viem - 0xE43F591AD474ca29deB4d0C89702539d66849b7F\r\n✅ Hardhat Ethers6 - 0x338d3f6d02440e29c1E7D2362FBFC266930aB14b\r\n✅ Foundry - 0xb81e538ed2394b2494608c283a557f0a9a4b9301\r\n\r\nMumbai\r\n❌ Hardhat Viem - (Tx Hangs - 0x14394d044ce5f05f6f233b418b25506415690b7d78e1df0d366ed18c74b1c477 but not deployed)\r\n❌ Hardhat Ethers6 - (Script Hangs - No Tx Hash)\r\n✅ Foundry - 0xbC7D321D31e64733Db7a1e4C9dD33941D68fEbB7\r\n```\n\n### Minimal reproduction steps\n\n1. npx hardhat init\r\n2. Typescript or Typescript with viem\r\n3. Configure hardhat.config.ts with proper networks (https://rpc.ankr.com/polygon, https://rpc.ankr.com/polygon_mumbai, https://rpc.ankr.com/eth_goerli)\r\n4. Try deploying the contract and see isues\n\n### Search terms\n\n_No response_",
